# QiziShell dev restart

After editing files that affect the running Electron app (`main.js`, `gateway-ws.js`, `app.js`, `preload.js`, `index.html`, `style.css`, etc.):

1. Restart with the detached script (do **not** use bare `npm start` in a Cursor background shell — the shell teardown kills Electron).
2. Wait for the script to finish and confirm it prints `QiziShell started`.
3. Only ask the user to start manually if `npm run restart` exits non-zero.

```bash
npm run restart
```

（在仓库根目录 `~/Documents/Code/qizi-shell` 执行。）

Use `block_until_ms` ≥ 8000 so the verify loop can complete. Do **not** set `block_until_ms: 0`.

Log file: `$TMPDIR/qizi-shell-dev.log` (or `/tmp/qizi-shell-dev.log`).
